<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hem4" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hem,</orth> vb. to cry hem: <cit><quote>these burrs are in my heart. H. them away,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.3.18" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 3, 18</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>now play me Nestor; h. and stroke thy beard,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 1.3.165" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 3, 165</bibl></cit> (Ff <emph>hum</emph>). <cit><quote>and --s and beats her heart,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 4.5.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 5, 5</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>